Text: Where are 19 episodes in the first series, you have only got 12. Any hope for the missing 7?

Richy83, where in the hell do you get your information?

People, there are only 12 episodes. You can confirm this on wikipedia.

Well, Yidio and some similar sites are listing the current season as part of season 1 ... but as you can see on IMDB (at http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1785123/episodes ) there are 12 episodes in season 1.

There are 19 episodes, as listed on A&E's site:

http://www.aetv.com/storage-wars/episode-guide/season-1/

Wikipedia is only as up to date as people put in.

Also, it was aired in a different order than listed on the site.  This torrent has them in the order they were aired.

First 4 were aired 1, 3, 2, 4, so if you try to match them with the descriptions, 2 and 3 are flipped.  Also, 5, 6, 7 aired in the order 6, 7, 5, so those need to be rotated too. The rest are ok.

Episodes 13+ had been posted (erroneously) as season 2.
Any chance that we can get all 19 episodes? I have 1-12, 15-17. I need episodes 13, 14, 18, & 19 PLEASE?????
